name: UI KIT
description:
Free and open source Ui Kit with ready-to-use elements for building your future designs.


The components include:

  • Tags
  • Accordions
  • Buttons
  • Checkboxes & Radio
  • Modals
  • Notifications
  • Switches
  • Textareas
  • Select
  • Rating
  • Tabs
  • Menus
  • Inputs
  • Table


If you have any feedback, please feel free to contact me at irawinterman@gmail.com or via Linkedin
